      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·007.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">凱風.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>凱風自南，吹彼棘心；
棘心夭夭，母氏劬勞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The genial wind from the south
Blows on the heart of that jujube tree,
Till that heart looks tender and beautiful.
What toil and pain did our mother endure!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-beifeng-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
