      <prop type="x-translation-ref">凱風.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>睍睆黃鳥，載好其音；
有子七人，莫慰母心。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The beautiful yellow birds
Give forth their pleasant notes.
We are seven sons,
And cannot compose our mother's heart.</seg>
      </tuv>
